  questions:
  - question: "Gece deprem olursa ilk yap\u0131lmas\u0131 gereken nedir?"
    answers:
    - Pencereden bakmak
    - "Ayakkab\u0131 aramak"
    - "Ba\u015F\u0131n\u0131 koruyup g\xFCvenli pozisyon almak"
    - "I\u015F\u0131klar\u0131 a\xE7maya ko\u015Fmak"
    correctIndex: 2
  - question: "Yata\u011F\u0131n yan\u0131nda ne bulundurmak faydal\u0131d\u0131r?"
    answers:
    - Oyun konsolu
    - "A\u011F\u0131r kutular"
    - "El feneri ve deprem \xE7antas\u0131"
    - "Cam e\u015Fya"
    correctIndex: 2
  - question: "Deprem s\u0131ras\u0131nda dolap yan\u0131nda dururken neye dikkat
      edilmelidir?"
    answers:
    - "Kapaklar\u0131 a\xE7mak"
    - Aynaya bakmak
    - "Dolab\u0131n sabit olup olmad\u0131\u011F\u0131na"
    - "K\u0131yafet se\xE7mek"
    correctIndex: 2
